    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Scientists who specialize in the science of numbers, magnitudes, quantities expressed symbolically, and forms and figures, including their interrelationships and the operations performed on them.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
